            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 133276,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um elemento presente em quase todas as páginas da web são os links (também conhecidos como hyperlinks). Eles são elementos clicáveis que te levam para outra página.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt; &#xA;&lt;head&gt; &#xA; &lt;style&gt; &#xA;body { &#xA;  background: linear-gradient(to right, slateblue, lightblue); &#xA;  color: white; &#xA;  font-family: 'Trebuchet MS'; &#xA;  text-align: center; &#xA;} &#xA; &#xA;a { &#xA;  color: white; &#xA;} &#xA; &lt;/style&gt; &#xA;&lt;/head&gt; &#xA;&lt;body&gt; &#xA; &lt;h1&gt;Example link&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;a &#xA;  href=&quot;https://example.com&quot;&gt;Click here&lt;/a&gt; &#xA;&lt;/body&gt; &#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "a",
            "id": 133270,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em HTML, os links são criados com a tag <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>, que significa \"âncora\". <br />Tente completar o código.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Example link\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Click here\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"26\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"36\" /><option startIndex=\"36\" endIndex=\"40\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"[a]\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"[\\a]\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> seguido de <code>Click here</code> e finalmente <code>&lt;/a&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "href",
            "id": 133260,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Agora, precisamos indicar para onde o link deve levar quando clicado. <br />Dentro da tag de abertura, adicione o atributo <code>href</code> com o link.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Example link\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://example.com&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Click here\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"52\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>href=\"https://example.com\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Attributes",
            "id": 133258,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><code>href</code> (ou referência de hipertexto) é um <strong>atributo</strong>. Atributos fornecem informações extras sobre a tag e vão dentro da tag de abertura.</p><p>Um atributo href começa com a palavra <code>href</code>, seguida por um sinal de igual, e uma URL entre aspas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Example link\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://example.com&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Click here\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"30\" /><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"52\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>href</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>\"https://example.com\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Create link",
            "id": 133305,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Monte o código completo. Use este exemplo como referência: <code>&lt;a href=\"URL\"&gt; Content&lt;/a&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Example link\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"h1\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://example.com&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Click here\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"52\" /><option startIndex=\"52\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"63\" /><option startIndex=\"63\" endIndex=\"67\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;link&gt;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;a</code> seguido de <code>href=\"https://example.com\"</code> e depois <code>&gt;</code>, <code>Click here</code>, <code>&lt;/a&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
